25
00:01:23,640 --> 00:01:25,340
 Sure, almost unanimously.

26
00:01:25,340 --> 00:01:27,240
 Who did what unanimously?

27
00:01:27,240 --> 00:01:28,840
 The class father to me.

28
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:32,880
 Sam, Henry's been elected to wipe out his class debt this year.

29
00:01:32,880 --> 00:01:37,880
 [laughter]

30
00:01:37,880 --> 00:01:38,980
 You were?

31
00:01:38,980 --> 00:01:40,640
 She was, I don't know.

32
00:01:40,640 --> 00:01:42,900
 Everything's just suddenly going swell.

33
00:01:42,900 --> 00:01:45,280
 And you were elected unanimously?

34
00:01:45,280 --> 00:01:46,180
 Well, practically.

35
00:01:46,180 --> 00:01:48,280
 And then the school photographer took a picture.

36
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:50,040
