51
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:39,580
 14?

52
00:02:39,580 --> 00:02:41,080
 14?

53
00:02:41,080 --> 00:02:44,080
 Yeah. But in the picture, I was in the first row, Father.

54
00:02:44,080 --> 00:02:48,400
 Well, it's too late now, but you're going down and get a haircut.

55
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:50,200
