00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:21,600
 And here's the one they call the Yale Bowl.

153
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:24,400
 No, I don't think my mother--

154
00:06:24,400 --> 00:06:27,520
 in fact, I don't think anybody would care for that one.

155
00:06:27,520 --> 00:06:28,640
 What's this one?

