176
00:07:15,580 --> 00:07:17,620
 Would you mind holding your head still?

177
00:07:17,620 --> 00:07:18,380
 I wasn't looking at her.

178
00:07:18,380 --> 00:07:20,020
 I was looking at that man go up the ladder.

